re to Start","description":"Start with the Trial Balance to confirm the books tie out. Then read the Profit & Loss for the period and the Balance Sheet for the date. Use AR and AP Aging to chase money, GRNI for received-not-invoiced exposure, Period Close to lock a period, and Bank Reconciliation to match your entries to a bank statement. Pick any tile above to dive in.","side":"top"}}]}"""
